body:
@zcbenz I'm trying to figure out the last marked issue, where for a refresh the test window goes blank, but I haven't been able to solve it yet.

What I did notice though and it may be related, that if I disable hardware acceleration (with `app.disableHardwareAcceleration()`) to use the software path, and I create a browser window (not necessarily offscreen) and I destroy it (with `w.destroy`), after that when I create an offscreen browser window it won't run with a software output device, but it will use the GPU path. Any idea why this could be?

Note, that both of the above issues are only happening on macOS. On Windows it works fine.
